msgctxt "724"
msgid "Man in a Suit"
msgstr "Hombre Trajeado"

msgctxt "728"
msgid "Kiryu"
msgstr "Kiryu"

msgctxt "72_Man in a Suit"
msgid "Head up the stairs in the alley 'round back and tear Sky\\r\n"\n"Finance to shreds. We're not leaving until we haul out every last document they've got."
msgstr "Sube las escaleras en el callejón de atrás y haz pedazos el Sky\\r \n"\n"Finance. No nos iremos hasta que saquemos hasta el último documento que tengan."

msgctxt "84_Man in a Suit"
msgid "And whatever they try and say, just tell them we're under\\r\n"\n"orders from the district attorney's office. That's all they\\r\n"\n"need to know. Now get a move on."
msgstr "Y lo que sea que intenten decir, diles que estamos bajo órdenes\\r\n"\n" de la oficina del fiscal del distrito. Eso es todo\\r\n"\n" lo que necesitan saber. Ahora, muévete."

msgctxt "96_Kiryu"
msgid "(The DA? I wonder what happened.)"
msgstr "(¿El Agente de Distrito? Me pregunto qué pasó.)"

